panels.content: Corona Data Scraper Project: https://github.com/CSSEGISandData/COVID-19 NB: Data Feeds are constantly changing so expect inconsistencies around Active/Recovered cases whilst this is resolved

targets.query: Select last(cases) as time, time as timestamp from covid19

SELECT sum("cases") AS "Cases", sum("deaths") AS "Deaths", sum("active") AS "Active", sum("recovered") AS "Recovered" FROM "covid19" WHERE ("state" !~ /./ AND "county" !~ /./ AND "countryname" =~ /^$Country$/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(none)

panels.description: These are running total's rather than calculating active cases etc.

targets.query: SELECT sum("cases") AS "Total Cases" FROM "covid19" WHERE ("country" =~ /^$Country$/ AND "state" !~ /./ AND "county" !~ /./) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(none)
SELECT sum("cases")/sum("population") as "Population Infected" FROM "covid19" WHERE $timeFilter and "state" !~ /./ and ("countryname" =~ /^$Country$/) GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(none)

panels.description: These are running total's rather than calculating active cases etc.

targets.query: SELECT sum("deaths")/(sum("cases")-sum("active")) as "Mortality Rate" FROM "covid19" WHERE $timeFilter and  ("countryname" =~ /^$Country$/ AND "state" !~ /./ AND "county" !~ /./) GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(none)

targets.query: SELECT  sum("cases") -  (sum("active") +sum("deaths")) AS "Recovered" FROM "covid19" WHERE ("countryname" =~ /^$Country$/ AND "state" !~ /./ AND "county" !~ /./) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(none)

SELECT 1-(sum("deaths")/(sum("cases")-sum("active"))) as "Recovery Rate" FROM "covid19" WHERE $timeFilter and  ("countryname" =~ /^$Country$/ AND "state" !~ /./ AND "county" !~ /./) GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(none)

SELECT sum("cases") -  (sum("active") +sum("deaths")) AS "Recovered" FROM "covid19" WHERE ("countryname" =~ /^$Country$/ AND "county" !~ /./ AND "state" !~ /./) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time(1d), "geohash", "countryname" fill(none)
SELECT sum("deaths") FROM "covid19" WHERE ("country" =~ /^$Country$/ AND "county" !~ /./ AND "state" !~ /./) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval), "country" fill(none)

SELECT  sum("cases") -  (sum("active") +sum("deaths")) AS "Recovered" FROM "covid19" WHERE ("countryname" =~ /^$Country$/ AND "state" !~ /./ AND "county" !~ /./) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval), "countryname" fill(none)

SELECT sum("cases")/sum("population")*100000 as "Population Infected" FROM "covid19" WHERE $timeFilter and ("countryname" =~ /^$Country$/ AND "county" !~ /./ AND "state" !~ /./) GROUP BY time($__interval), "countryname" fill(none)

SELECT (sum("deaths")/sum("population"))*100000 as "Population Infected" FROM "covid19" WHERE $timeFilter and ("countryname" =~ /^$Country$/ AND "county" !~ /./ AND "state" !~ /./) GROUP BY time($__interval), "countryname" fill(none)

SELECT  non_negative_difference(sum("cases")) -  (non_negative_difference(sum("active")) + non_negative_difference(sum("deaths"))) AS "Recovered" FROM "covid19" WHERE ("countryname" =~ /^$Country$/ AND "state" !~ /./ AND "county" !~ /./) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval), "countryname" fill(none)
